#Any of the Python3 or Bash scripts can be used for the Phone Number replacement in HTML files. 
#Used Regular Expressions in both. 

#Bash Script
# A second command can be used if you prefer to have backup of your original html data.
#A single Pipeline of linux commands has been used for this replacement. 
Command: ./ChangePhoneNumber.sh
Result: Phone Numbers are Changed.

#Python3 Script:
Command: ./ChangePhoneNumber.py 
Input: <Directory Path of HTML Files>
Example: /var/www/
Result: Phone Numbers are Changed. 
